                       40 "LN/*=PARALAST" T)
                (for L inlines FIRSTLINE do (SHOWLINE L OFILE TOBJ) repeatuntil (EQ L LASTLINE)
                   finally (CL:WHEN (EQ LASTLINE (PANEBOTTOMLINE PANE))
